1- useRef is use to initialize the value of fadeAnimation is 0 means disable mode.
    const fadeAnimation = useRef(new Animated.Value(0)).current;
2- we use the safeAreaView to bounderies the content in the body of safeAreaView meas a container.

3-we are making two view in the container one for button and another for fading the content

4- we create two buton fadein and fadeout
5- onprss button we make an event function for performing the task of fading
        const FadeOut=()=>{
            Animated.timing(fadeAnimation,{
                toValue: 0,
                durations:3000
            }).start();
        };
